OL,3,CSalmon buried on Scottish beach
OL,4,Cillegally, campaign footage shows
OL,6,FFootage shows Whiteshore Cockles
OL,7,Fburying salmon on a beach four months
OL,8,Fafter the practice was made illegal in
OL,9,FScotland. The company says it is "not
OL,10,Fhappening at all" now but refused to
OL,11,Fcomment on the clip, ITV News Scotland
OL,12,FReporter Louise Scott reports.
OL,14,FThe Outer Hebrides are famed for their
OL,15,Fpowder white beaches and turquoise
OL,16,Fwaters, which line the chain of
OL,17,Fislands off Scotland's west coast.
OL,19,FBut on one of North Uist's idyllic
OL,20,Fbeaches lies a salmon graveyard.
