OL,4,Cillegally, campaign footage shows
OL,6,FA fish drier breaks down the salmon
OL,7,Fmortalities with heat turning them in
OL,8,Fto fish oil and fishmeal, which would
OL,9,Fbe a sustainable solution for the
OL,10,Fdisposal of salmon mortalities in the
OL,11,FWestern Isles.
OL,13,FWhen the derogation came to an end on
OL,14,FJanuary 31, 2024, it became illegal to
OL,15,Fbury the salmon.
OL,17,FBut footage given to us by Green
OL,18,Fenergy company and environmental
OL,19,Fcampaigners, Ecotricity, shows the
OL,20,Fcompany was still burying salmon four
OL,21,Fmonths later.
