OL,6,FThe filming, from May, shows lorries
OL,7,Ftipping huge amounts of salmon into a
OL,8,Fpit. The process appears to be
OL,9,Frepeated until all of the salmon is
OL,10,Fpiled high.
OL,12,FSeaweed is then dumped on top to cover
OL,13,Fit.
