OL,6,FWe took the footage to an independent
OL,7,Fexpert at Glasgow University.
OL,9,FDr Michell Bloor, a Lecturer in
OL,10,FEnvironmental Science and Risk, said:
OL,11,F"The burial of such large numbers of
OL,12,Ffish, in what appears to be an unlined
OL,13,Fsite, will result in large amounts of
OL,14,Fdecomposition products leaching into
OL,15,Fthe surrounding environment.
OL,17,F"These decomposition products will
OL,18,Finclude large amounts of nitrogen and
OL,19,Fphosphate, which could contribute to
OL,20,Fthe eutrophication of any associated
OL,21,Ffreshwater environment.
